# VITE_API_URL is intentionally NOT set here.
# api.ts dynamically picks the right base URL:
#   - localhost → http://localhost:3001 (direct, fast for desktop dev)
#   - LAN IP   → http://<LAN-IP>:5173  (via Vite proxy, works for phone QR scanning)
# Only set this if you need to point at a remote backend (e.g. staging).
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3001